Commit Message: Capture first working version (of admittedly second iteration over code)
Add example that uses a textual representation instead of bitmaps
Update package name, --scale instead of --speedup option, and fix tool name
Remove package.json from all things Node.js
Add support for speed and keypress_speed optional arguments
Apply a consistent naming convention for all functions and methods that adjust timing

Apply several critical changes

* Introduce dedicated exception to indicate malformed pragmas
* Make regular expression more accepting but then raise an exception on unrecognized pragmas.
* Update method selection in Controller
* Add method to parse floating point numbers while correctly raising an invalid pragma exception upon parse errors.
* Fix computation of sigma parameter for lognormal distribution
* Simplify configuration state of Animator and get rid of properties.
* Introduce method to create new event with adjusted speed.
* Similarly, adjust delay for keypresses with corresponding speed.
Add support for verbose option, incorporate extra perform() results
Add support for tracking minimum screen size in characters
Make classes configurable, return minimum screen size, automate setting of screen size in header
Add method to strip ANSI escape codes
